Name: Description
Commuting: The share of individuals who worked in the last week (excluding those who work at home), by the reported time it usually takes to get from home to work.

Name: Source Notes
Commuting: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey 1-Year Estimates, Table B08012 (2012-2019, 2021); retrieved from https://data.census.gov/.

Name: Notes
Commuting: Please note, we do not report 2020 American Community Survey 1-year estimates. Due to disruptions and biases in data collection during 2020, the Census Bureau released the “experimental” 1-year estimates for 2020 and advises against comparing against estimates from prior or future years.
